<pb facs="1038369" n="142"/>
<opener><lb/>Viro Illustrissimo et Doctissimo
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>N. B.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Postquam feliciter <rs key="place_GEB-alpena" type="place">Alpes</rs> transgressus, et hesterna die salvus
         <lb/>et incolumis hic <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> redux factus sum, officii mei erga
         <lb/>Te ratio postulare videtur, ut quam primum de valetudine
         <lb/>Tua Te interrogem, Tibique inclusam hanc <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patrui</rs> mei <rs key="B_991170515017605501" type="letter">epistolam</rs>
<lb/>transmittam. Gaudebo si scivero, Te optima valetudine
         <lb/><del>h<gap/>i </del>hucusque semper gavisum fuisse et adhucdum gaudere.
         <lb/>De pristini erga me favoris Tui constantia nullus dubito, ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>limque credas, me pariter de debita Tibi observantia nihil
         <lb/>remisisse. Significo Tibi, me <subst><del>compara</del><add>attuli</add></subst>sse <rs key="biblio_RC6TN74M" type="biblio">libellum</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-100704514" type="person">Wetstenii</rs>,
         <lb/>cui titulus, Flores Eloquenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quemque data occasione
         <lb/>mittam. Si qui sunt qui<del> de</del> mei forte apud Te meminerint,
         <lb/>eos cultus mei certiores facere ne graveris. </p><closer><salute>Vale et fave.</salute>
                  <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1717-10-30">30. 8bris. 1717</date>.</dateline></closer>
<lb/><postscript><p>Dego apud D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenum</rs>, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>S.</abbr> Giacomo in Casa Capodilista.</p></postscript>
</div></body></text></TEI>